OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FThe US Secretary of State has met with
OL,7,FPope Leo XIV at the Vatican days after
OL,8,FDonald Trump levelled another
OL,9,Fcriticism at the pontiff over the
OL,10,Fongoing war in Iran.
OL,12,FMarco Rubio, a practicing Catholic,
OL,13,Farrived in Rome on Thursday for a two-
OL,14,Fday visit to Italy and the Vatican,
OL,15,Fduring which he will also meet Prime
OL,16,FMinister Giorgia Meloni and Foreign
OL,17,FMinister Antonio Tajani.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
