PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FHe spoke with the Pope about the US
OL,7,Fwar in Iran, and "topics of mutual
OL,8,Finterest in the Western Hemisphere",
OL,9,FState Department spokesperson Tommy
OL,10,FPigott said.
OL,12,F"The meeting underscored the strong
OL,13,Frelationship between the United States
OL,14,Fand the Holy See and their shared
OL,15,Fcommitment to promoting peace and
OL,16,Fhuman dignity," Pigott said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FThe secretary of state also met with
OL,7,FCardinal Pietro Parolin, where they
OL,8,Fdiscussed "efforts to achieve a
OL,9,Fdurable peace in the Middle East" and
OL,10,Fthe "enduring partnership between the
OL,11,FUS and the Holy See in advancing
OL,12,Freligious freedom".
OL,14,FRubio's meeting with the Pope was
OL,15,Fcomplicated at the last minute by the
OL,16,FUS president, who claimed on Monday
OL,17,Fthat the first American-born pontiff
OL,18,Fis supporting Iran's nuclear
OL,19,Fcapabilities and "endangering" a lot
OL,20,Fof people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,F"The Pope would rather talk about the
OL,7,Ffact that it's okay for Iran to have a
OL,8,Fnuclear weapon," Trump told
OL,9,Fconservative commentator Hugh Hewitt
OL,10,Fin a radio interview.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"And I don't think that's very good. I
OL,18,Fthink he's endangering a lot of
OL,19,FCatholics and a lot of people."
OL,26,@pD@PO]{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
