OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FLeo has pushed back against Trump's
OL,7,Fclaims, stating that the church has
OL,8,Falways been against nuclear weapons
OL,9,Fand that he is preaching the biblical
OL,10,Fmessage of peace.
OL,12,FThe Pope has never said Iran should
OL,13,Fobtain nuclear weapons.
OL,15,F"The mission of the church is to
OL,16,Fpreach the Gospel, to preach peace. If
OL,17,Fsomeone wants to criticise me for
OL,18,Fannouncing the Gospel, let him do it
OL,19,Fwith the truth," the Pope said on
OL,20,FTuesday.
OL,26,@{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,F"The whole concept of war has to be
OL,7,Freevaluated in terms today," the Pope
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,F"And I always believe that it's much
OL,11,Fbetter to enter into dialogue than to
OL,12,Flook for arms."
OL,14,FBoth Meloni and Tajani, who Rubio will
OL,15,Fmeet on Friday, have defended the Pope
OL,16,Fagainst Trump and criticised the US-
OL,17,FIsrael war on Iran as illegal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
