PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FMeloni was the only leader of a
OL,7,FEuropean Union country invited to
OL,8,FTrump's second inauguration, but her
OL,9,Fcomments caused him to tell Italian
OL,10,Fnewspaper Corriere della Sera: "I
OL,11,Fthought she had courage. I was wrong."
OL,13,FTrump's comments about the Pope are
OL,14,Fnot new, with him describing the
OL,15,Fpontiff as "WEAK on crime" and
OL,16,F"terrible for foreign policy" in a
OL,17,FTruth Social post on April 12.
OL,19,FHe later posted an image appearing to
OL,20,Fdepict himself as Jesus Christ, which
OL,21,Fwas then deleted following backlash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
