CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FThe next day, the Pope told
OL,7,Fjournalists during a trip to Algeria:
OL,8,F"I have no fear of the Trump
OL,9,Fadministration, or speaking out loudly
OL,10,Fof the message of the Gospel, which is
OL,11,Fwhat I believe I am here to do."
OL,13,FLeo also said the world was being
OL,14,F"ravaged by a handful of tyrants" who
OL,15,Fspend billions on war during a speech
OL,16,Fin Cameroon on April 16, in what was
OL,17,Fwidely interpreted to be a reference
OL,18,Fto Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778220038
OL,3,CRubio meets with Pope Leo amid Trump's
OL,4,Ccriticism over Iran war
OL,6,FThe Rev Antonio Spadaro,
OL,7,Fundersecretary in the Vatican's
OL,8,Fculture office, said Rubio's trip
OL,9,Fwasn't to "convert" the Pope to
OL,10,FTrump's side, but that Washington had
OL,11,F"come to acknowledge ... that (Leo's)
OL,12,Fvoice carries weight in the world that
OL,13,Fcannot simply be dismissed".
OL,15,F"The situation created by president
OL,16,FTrump's remarks required a high-level,
OL,17,Fdirect intervention, conducted in the
OL,18,Fproper language of diplomacy: a
OL,19,Fsemantic corrective to a narrative of
OL,20,Ffrontal conflict with the church," he
OL,21,Fwrote in an essay this week.
